               Where are sites with weather satellite imagery?

   Obtain GOES-8, GOES-10, GMS-5, and METEOSAT-7 weather satellite data by
                                anonymous ftp

   Where are the weather satellites located? Use NASA's J-Track utility to
                                  find out.
